                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.111 Quota 56/276: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Consul General at Amsterdam</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Lee</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-07-28T10:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 28, 1940—10 a.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>128. Your 340, 17th. You are authorized to issue nonpreference visas under the
                    Netherland quota in urgent cases to nonquota relatives of American citizens.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Welles</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
